==English==

===Transitive verb===
{{en-infl-reg-other-e|dereferenc|e}}

# {{complang}} To dereference a memory location is to obtain the value stored therein in a context which interprets the value obtained as the address of a memory location.
# {{complang}} (in the context of computer languages which support [[pointer|pointers]]) To access the thing to which a pointer points.

